Listen, I don't care what conclusion you come to.  I did put alot of 
thought into Mustex, Stallex, and Rhesus and don't want to see them 
go. And I also very much want to incorporate "Transformers: Robots in 
Disguise into this rpg but no matter what happens I don't want to go 
down in history as "The RPGer who never offically posted" so I just 
want a robot here to post about, and I'm not about to take any of 
Yan's (even if from what I've gathered some of them are up for grabs I 
just don't know enough about them). So could we get this settled? If I 
get to keep Omega I want to have Optimus and Ultra duking it out 
pronto, got it (I don't mean to sound rude just assertive and somewhat 
annoyed).
